Just finished reading Praying Upside Down. This book offers creative alternatives for praying outside our usual prayer routine. Read it!
If you haven't read Unbroken, you should. It is an incredible story of one man's journey from Olympic fame to a POW camp in Japan to God.
When I'm reading a book, I'm not trying to ignore you...it just happens naturally! Reading Passion and Purity by Elisabeth Elliot!
Read The Total Money Makeover by Dave Ramsey. It is challenging and potentially life changing for all ages!
When you're having a bad day, read the Bible, pray, then go home and watch #BoyMeetsWorld!
